data.description: Updated 4 bedroom home with 2 primary bedrooms. Kitchen has a lot of cabinets and counter space along with a half bath just around the corner. Large dining area with bay window. The main primary bedroom is huge with a faux fireplace and has a door leading to the backyard. Other primary bedroom also has a faux fireplace and is very large w/built-ins. Secondary bedrooms are a nice size also. Storage throughout and cedar closet.  Fencing is less than 6 months old. This home is warm and inviting and waiting for you. Seller is offering $1,000 toward closing costs.
